org.jemmy.interfaces

Interface Shifter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ScrollTrack

    public interface Shifter
    Interface represents a "handle" for shifting value/position of owning Shiftable control in unit and block increments/decrements.
    Author:
    ineverov
    See Also:
    Shiftable
